<h2 class="bold font-l">Stan Lee [Civil War]</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Stan Lee cameos as a FedEx delivery man. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TheCameo" class='trope-example-link'>The Cameo</a></p>
